<h2 id="comments">Comments</h2>

<div id="c1">
<p>As a (west) Philadelphian, I can definitely see you fitting in here. Your interest in social activism has a natural fit here; I believe we lead the nation in number of non-profits organizations.</p>

<p>Lunch is on me if you are ever in town. (I&#8217;ve used enough of your freely available software that it seems only fair.)</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://db79.com">Shawn Medero</a>
